    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Designed schematics and layouts for mixed-signal analog blocks in TSMC
        180nm CMOS using Cadence Virtuoso, including comparators and an
        asynchronous flash ADC for the BIRD chip.
      </li>
      <li>
        Built and verified analog switch layouts; contributed to top-level chip
        integration and pad ring formatting.
      </li>
      <li>
        Validated circuit performance via Monte Carlo and PEX simulations to catch
        yield and process-variation issues before tape-out.
      </li>
    </ul>

